Package it.polimi.ingsw.interfaces

Class ViewObservable

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.interfaces.ViewObservable
Direct Known Subclasses:
View, VirtualView
public abstract class ViewObservable
extends java.lang.Object
Base Class for View part of MVC. It is implemented by View and VirtualView. Contains different observers for every event generated by user that Controller should handle
